00:34:51,339 --> 00:34:52,960
I'm running late.

462
00:35:01,699 --> 00:35:05,239
Your Lordship, pardon my tardiness. I drank too much.

463
00:35:05,239 --> 00:35:07,340
Please punish me.

464
00:35:07,340 --> 00:35:11,240
That's not the only thing you've committed.

465
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:19,819
Did I lose my temper after drinking?

466
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:22,160
Do you remember nothing?

467
00:35:26,579 --> 00:35:31,638
I can only remember that you said you would teach me the Northern Liang language in person.

468
00:35:31,638 --> 00:35:33,360
I'll be studious.

469
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,260
I won't let you down.

470
00:35:40,299 --> 00:35:41,618
Don't be late again.

471
00:35:41,619 --> 00:35:43,019
Noted.

472
00:35:43,739 --> 00:35:48,899
Your Lordship, what are we studying today?

473
00:35:49,469 --> 00:35:53,639
You will stay in my study to learn common words in Northern Liang.

474
00:35:53,700 --> 00:35:57,600
You are to memorize 100 words this morning.

475
00:35:57,600 --> 00:35:59,900
There will be a test this afternoon.

476
00:35:59,900 --> 00:36:02,759
Yes, Your Lordship. I will work hard.

477
00:36:09,699 --> 00:36:11,779
See you, Your Lordship.

478
